        #(...)
        
    @classmethod()
    def from_text_file(cls, filename):
        #extract all the parameters from the text file
        return cls(*params)        



@statix Method
static method doesn't have the callling object passed into it as teh first parameter. 
This means that it doesn't have accessto the rest of the class or instance aat all

