we create an add_time function that is a pure function ( does not modify any of the objects passed to it as parameters and it has no side effects 
such as updated global variables, displaying a value or getting user input. 

def add_time (t1,t2): 
    h = t1.hours + t2.hours
    m = t1.minutes + t2.minutes
    s = t1.seconds + t2.seconds
    sum_t = MyTime(h, m, s) 
    return sum_t 



